name: Donovan Birch
profile_summary: Our user is a 32-year-old man with pronouns He/Him/His, 6'1" tall and a white Caucasian. He is graduated from the University of California, Berkeley and is currently working as a Software Developer in the technology industry. Originally from Sacramento, California, he now lives in Los Angeles. A straight man, with an INTJ personality type, who labels himself as a Libra and Agnostic, he is politically liberal and is interested in a long-term, monogamous relationship. In terms of lifestyle, he is physically active, drinks occasionally, but doesn't smoke or use marijuana or other drugs. He is a dog lover with no children, but he wishes to have some in the near future. You'll find him running, reading, gaming or cooking in his free time - interests that reflect his core values of creativity, fitness, knowledge, and ambition. He is fluent in both English and Spanish. His ideal dating location is his current residence - Los Angeles, California.
